import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import * as C from './styles'

type Props = {
    title: string,
    description: string,
    icon: string,
    path: string
}

export const SidebarItem = ({ title, description, icon, path }: Props) => {
    return (
        <C.Container>
            <Link to={path}>
                <C.Info>
                    <C.Title>{title}</C.Title>
                    <C.Description>{description}</C.Description>
                </C.Info>
                <C.IconArea>

                </C.IconArea>
                <C.Point></C.Point>
            </Link>
        </C.Container>    
    )
}
